
Yoga Spin GUI
=============

Switching touchpad for Yoga laptops when lid position changes, GUI for enabling/disabling finger touch screen if used with stylus.

Features:
 * Run on startup, systray entry with context menu available
 * When lid moves to tablet mode makes sure touch screen is enabled and starts OnBoard touch keyboard. Also disables touch pad.
 * When lid moves to laptop mode terminates OnBoard touch keyboard and enables touch pad.
 * Dialog for enabling and disabling touch screen for purpose of working only with the stylus.


Building debian package:
------------------------

`# dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot`

Adding changelog entry using `dch` from package devscripts:

`# dch -v X.Y.Z "message"`
`# dch --release`



